# Adak Enterprise – Tathya Mitra Kendra Website: Implementation Plan

## Stack
| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend (Public) | HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JS (bilingual i18n) |
| Backend | Node.js + Express |
| Database | SQLite (via `better-sqlite3`) |
| Admin Panel | HTML5 + CSS3 + Vanilla JS (protected routes) |
| SMS/WhatsApp stub | Twilio SDK (stub mode) |
| File uploads | Multer |
| Auth | JWT + bcrypt |

