## Key Features per Phase

### Phase 1 – Database + Backend API
- SQLite tables: services, sales, shop_info, content, users, notifications
- REST API endpoints for CRUD operations
- JWT auth middleware
- File upload for banners

### Phase 2 – Public Website
- 4 pages: Home, Services, About, Contact
- Bilingual English/Bengali toggle
- Dynamic data from API (services, shop info)
- Contact form

### Phase 3 – Admin Panel
- Login with JWT
- Dashboard: due counter, recent sales
- Sales entry CRUD + status (pending/done)
- Service management CRUD
- Shop info editor
- Content/banner management
- Notification trigger (SMS stub via Twilio)

### Phase 4 – Bonus
- WhatsApp float button
- Export to Excel
- Customer history
